CASE ANNOUNCEMENTS

May 14, 2014

[Cite as 05/14/2014 Case Announcements, 2014-Ohio-2021.]

MERIT DECISIONS WITHOUT OPINIONS

2014-0293. Morris v. Marsh.

In Mandamus. On complaint in mandamus. Upon consideration of respondent’s suggestion of mootness and on S.Ct.Prac.R. 12.04 determination, cause dismissed.

O’Connor, C.J., and Pfeifer, O’Donnell, Lanzinger, Kennedy, French, and O’Neill, JJ., concur.
